title: Disabled students positive about Radboud University (Radboud Universiteit)
text: ( Source : Radboud Universiteit) Students with a functional disability express an above average level of satisfaction with the supervision, understanding and facilities at Radboud University . Only students in Wageningen top RU in satisfaction
